        "rendered": "<p>Faculty Research Mentor Spotlight: Kimberly Barchard, Ph.D. MAR. 10, 2022 Kimberly Barchard, Ph.D., Professor of Psychology in the College of Liberal Arts. OUR proudly presented the 2021 Outstanding Faculty Mentor Award to Dr. Barchard for her record of excellence in inspiring, influencing, supporting, and mentoring undergraduate researchers in their professional development, career training, and educational [&hellip;]</p>\n",
